{"tid":967492,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點先識到鍾意一大班開Party的朋友？","createTime":"2019-01-03T13:52:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-04T14:22:00.000Z","uid":63048,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"85a0c6daf496a392588d00d4435caf20c96cdc90","tid":967492,"uid":63048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T13:52:57.000Z","msg":"大學時期就比較多Party 去，最好個點係除咗自己識的朋友之外，周不時會有新的人加入，咁大家個社交氣氛會唔錯。<br />\n出到來做嘢之後，圈子好似唔易增長，少咗好多 Party 去。如果同同事大家年紀又差得遠，又要顧忌形象，好難玩得埋。<br />\n各位如果每星期都有Party 的話，其實班朋友的來源係邊？再唔去多啲呢類場合，覺得自己可能會有社交缺乏症。"},{"pid":"da435a8df6d6a6c41754cd8bdcf5e5bf52aa6251","tid":967492,"uid":52122,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T13:54:00.000Z","msg":"連登tg谷"},{"pid":"3e1319459f72af34db4d08e0ab9b0cafca62a440","tid":967492,"uid":63048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da435a8df6d6a6c41754cd8bdcf5e5bf52aa6251","tid":967492,"uid":52122,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T13:54:00.000Z","msg":"連登tg谷"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T14:19:17.000Z","msg":"有邊個好推介？最好大家都玩得的，同埋唔好歧視new joiner"},{"pid":"109abffe8f685329328b412f20e68dd2ff18dded","tid":967492,"uid":225295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T14:24:56.000Z","msg":"麥當勞ok?"},{"pid":"d1dc67f1b3eef68de4e1a071eba028135b16bc18","tid":967492,"uid":63048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"109abffe8f685329328b412f20e68dd2ff18dded","tid":967492,"uid":225295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T14:24:56.000Z","msg":"麥當勞ok?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T14:26:10.000Z","msg":"都 ok ga 唔好笑金鍾聚會啦，其實氣氛幾好。"},{"pid":"c0ed8eb7c1e1ee97041aa6c235b548d0c686f519","tid":967492,"uid":63048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T04:57:41.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5f2b8f3e3e1151c0a9c82a8a389b449a2b2e721c","tid":967492,"uid":59492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T06:48:57.000Z","msg":"跟我去活動就會識到"},{"